name: Yogi
additional_notices:
The following token has a variable tax function on the smart contract to change tax rates post deployment.
Do your own research and be careful if you are trading this token.

description.en:
Yogi is a new meme token project that has recently launched on decentralized exchange Sushiswap , The project has a total supply of 100 hundred  million tokens, and ownership has been renounced. and Liquidity is locked for 1 year.

On the Path of Non-Extinction, slowly I perfect my power.

Yogi  is a community meme token The token is completely community driven and was fair launched. Every trade continues toward automatically generating liquidity locked inside of Sushiswap's LP. Holders earn passive rewards through static reflection as they watch their balance of "ETH" indefinitely grow.

The project is run by a team of volunteers and paid employees, led by the founder Leon, also known as ilon . Leon is a 33-year-old crypto entrepreneur from the England with a background in cryptocurrency.
